                    "value": "<p>the exception of <persName>Mary<add>?</add></persName> who is<lb/> again sick.</p>\n            <p><persName>Jesse Nashes<add>?</add></persName> wife, <persName>Clara</persName>,\n                is<lb/> dead; she died last <date>Tuesday</date><lb/> is it not very sad?</p>\n            <p>This letter is <add>?</add> so good bye<lb/> Mama &amp; <persName>Delia</persName>\n                send Love &amp;<lb/> a <hi rend=\"underline\">little <add>?</add></hi> comes from</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Your friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">L. L. Lazarus</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>Write soon</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
